                            	  1369: *
                            	  1370: * ===== Test text byte following the call to this subroutine. If it
                            	  1371: *	equals the byte pointed to by A0, return to the code following
                            	  1372: *	the call. If they are not equal, branch to the point
                            	  1373: *	indicated by the offset byte following the text byte.
                            	  1374: *
